    <thetext>Description of problem:

The gmp build system drops the LDFLAGS hardening flags, and the installed DSOs are not using BIND_NOW as a result.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):

gmp-6.1.1-1.fc25.x86_64

How reproducible:

Always.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. eu-readelf -d /lib64/libgmp.so.10.3.1 | grep NOW

Actual results:

(no output)

Expected results:

BIND_NOW flags shown.</thetext>
